      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Al Husayn Bin Muhammad, from Moala Bin Muhammad, from Al Washa, from Aban, from Ibn Muzarab, ",
          "Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> has said: ‘The one who accuses his wife before he copulates with her would be whipped the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>), and she would (still) be his wife’."
